Description: Redirection for lxc-list
 lxc-list will be deprecated in final 0.9, this patch adds a warning when
 lxc-ls is called as lxc-list (through the temporary symlink) and changes
 the default rendering to list similar options.
Author: St√©phane Graber <stgraber@ubuntu.com>
Origin: vendor
Forwarded: not-needed

Index: raring-lxc/src/lxc/lxc-ls
===================================================================
--- raring-lxc.orig/src/lxc/lxc-ls	2013-02-18 19:25:08.643504894 +0000
+++ raring-lxc/src/lxc/lxc-ls	2013-02-18 19:26:41.183503499 +0000
@@ -116,6 +116,13 @@
 
 args = parser.parse_args()
 
+# lxc-list is an alias for --fancy
+if sys.argv[0].endswith("lxc-list"):
+    args.fancy = True
+    print("WARNING: lxc-list is deprecated, please use lxc-ls --fancy.")
+    print("         This symlink will be dropped in LXC 0.9 final.")
+    print("")
+
 # --active is the same as --running --frozen
 if args.active:
     if not args.state:
